name: Indigo Gold Chest
desc: "The Winners' Chest in the Indigo Plateau Conference gives a chance to get rewards such as coins, arena coins, friendship level enhancement items, potential training materials, trinket awakening and Star Up items and other items."

name: Legendary Held Item Chest
desc: After opening, you can choose one from Fiery Claws, Resonance Element, Immortal Shield, Dynamax Band, Huge Power Bracer, PokéFlute, Power Ring, Silph Scope, Professor's Mask, Gem Bracelet,Mega Glasses, Mega Stickpin , Safety Goggles, Mega Watch, Dowsing Machine

name: Goldeen bait
desc: The bait made by imitating Goldeen, it is said that the material is very particular, can be used on Tidal Coast and Silent Swamp, slightly increasing the probability of the appearance of medium and high-level fish

name: Horsea bait
desc: The bait made by imitating Horsea, is said to be very delicious, can be used on Tidal Coasts, Silent Swamps, and Wandering Valleys. It slightly increases the probability of the appearance of medium and high-level fish.
desc_tw: 模仿墨海馬製作的魚餌，據說味道非常鮮美，可在潮汐海岸、寂夜沼澤、逆徊山谷使用，略微提升中高級魚的出現概率

desc_en: The bait made by imitating Dratini, is said to be able to attract fish with a radius of 1 km. It can be used on Tidal Coasts, Silent Swamps, and Wandering Valleys. It slightly increases the probability of the appearance of meduim and high-level fish.
desc_kr: 미뇽을 모방해 만든 미끼, 1km 근방의 물고기를 유인할 수 있다고 한다. 조석의 해안, 적야의 늪, 거꾸로 된 계곡에서 사용할 수 있으며, 고급 어종의 등장 확률이 소폭 증가한다.
